comments: The song originally peaked at No.5 in the Irish singles charts, before being re-released a year later. From here it peaked at No.1 and remained on the charts throughout the whole of 1979 and into 1980, eventually spending a total of 90 weeks in the Irish top 30 - the longest run by any song in Irish Chart history.
